# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s3_xuner.rpy:10
translate english ch1_s3_xuner_cf57d308:

    # tester "下一个，萧薰儿！"
    tester "Next, Xiao Xun'er!"

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s3_xuner.rpy:15
translate english ch1_s3_xuner_6909f9f7:

    # "喧闹的人群中，测试员的声音，再次响了起来。"
    "In the noisy crowd, the tester's voice rang out again."

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s3_xuner.rpy:17
translate english ch1_s3_xuner_f52f80d8:

    # "随着这有些清雅的名字响起，人群忽然的安静了下来，所有的视线，豁然转移。"
    "As this somewhat elegant name sounded, the crowd suddenly quieted down, and all eyes shifted abruptly."

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s3_xuner.rpy:25
translate english ch1_s3_xuner_6e20e27f:

    # "在众人视线汇聚之处，一位身着紫色衣裙的少女，正淡雅的站立，平静的稚嫩俏脸，并未因为众人的注目而改变分毫。"
    "At the spot where everyone's gazes converged, a young girl in a purple dress stood elegantly. Her calm, youthful face did not change in the slightest because of the crowd's attention."

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s3_xuner.rpy:27
translate english ch1_s3_xuner_aa072278:

    # "少女清冷淡然的气质，犹如清莲初绽，小小年纪，却已初具脱俗气质，难以想象，日后若是长大，少女将会如何的倾国倾城……"
    "The girl's cold and indifferent temperament was like a lotus just blooming. At such a young age, she already possessed an unworldly air. It was hard to imagine how breathtaking her beauty would be when she grew up..."

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s3_xuner.rpy:29
translate english ch1_s3_xuner_c3660245:

    # "这名紫裙少女，论起美貌与气质来，比先前的萧媚，无疑还要更胜上几分，也难怪在场的众人都是这般动作。"
    "This purple-dressed girl, in terms of beauty and temperament, was undoubtedly a few notches above Xiao Mei from before. It was no wonder everyone present reacted this way."

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s3_xuner.rpy:34
translate english ch1_s3_xuner_ebb05c23:

    # "莲步微移，名为萧薰儿的少女行到魔石碑之前，小手伸出，镶着黑金丝的紫袖滑落而下，露出一截雪白娇嫩的皓腕，然后轻触着石碑……"
    "Moving gracefully, the girl named Xiao Xun'er walked to the Magic Testing Monolith. She extended her small hand, her purple sleeve embroidered with black gold threads slipping down to reveal a segment of snow-white, tender wrist, and then lightly touched the monolith..."

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s3_xuner.rpy:39
translate english ch1_s3_xuner_41548b9c:

    # "微微沉静，石碑之上，刺眼的光芒再次绽放。"
    "After a brief silence, dazzling light blossomed once again on the monolith."

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s3_xuner.rpy:41
translate english ch1_s3_xuner_6efa8ee3:

    # tester "斗之气：九段！级别：高级！"
    tester "Dou Qi: 9th Stage! Rank: High!"

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s3_xuner.rpy:46
translate english ch1_s3_xuner_1fbbb64a:

    # "望着石碑之上的字体，场中陷入了一阵寂静。"
    "Looking at the characters on the monolith, the field fell into silence."

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s3_xuner.rpy:48
translate english ch1_s3_xuner_1e00cce1:

    # crowd "……竟然到九段了，真是恐怖！家族中年轻一辈的第一人，恐怕非薰儿小姐莫属了。"
    crowd "...It actually reached the 9th Stage, truly terrifying! The number one of the younger generation in the clan is undoubtedly Miss Xun'er."

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s3_xuner.rpy:50
translate english ch1_s3_xuner_868653a9:

    # "寂静过后，周围的少年，都是不由自主的咽了一口唾沫，眼神充满敬畏……"
    "After the silence, the surrounding boys all involuntarily gulped, their eyes filled with awe..."

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s3_xuner.rpy:53
translate english ch1_s3_xuner_6d5ebb47:

    # "斗之气，每位斗者的必经之路，初阶斗之气分一至十段，当体内斗之气到达十段之时，便能凝聚斗之气旋，成为一名受人尊重的斗者！"
    "Dou Qi, the inevitable path for every Dou Practitioner. Initial Dou Qi is divided into one to ten stages. When the Dou Qi in the body reaches the 10th Stage, one can condense a Dou Qi Cyclone and become a respected Dou Practitioner!"

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s3_xuner.rpy:58
translate english ch1_s3_xuner_601b0938:

    # "人群中，萧媚皱着浅眉盯着石碑前的紫裙少女，脸颊上闪过一抹嫉妒……"
    "In the crowd, Xiao Mei frowned slightly, staring at the purple-dressed girl in front of the monolith, a flash of jealousy crossing her cheeks..."

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s3_xuner.rpy:63
translate english ch1_s3_xuner_7208e386:

    # "望着石碑上的信息，一旁的中年测验员漠然的脸庞上竟然也是罕见的露出了一丝笑意，对着少女略微恭声道："
    "Looking at the information on the monolith, the indifferent face of the middle-aged tester beside it rarely revealed a hint of a smile, and he said somewhat respectfully to the girl:"

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s3_xuner.rpy:65
translate english ch1_s3_xuner_d46985bd:

    # tester "薰儿小姐，半年之后，你应该便能凝聚斗气之旋，如果你成功的话，那么以十四岁年龄成为一名真正的斗者，你是萧家百年内的第二人！"
    tester "Miss Xun'er, in half a year, you should be able to condense a Dou Qi Cyclone. If you succeed, becoming a true Dou Practitioner at the age of fourteen, you will be the second person in the Xiao Clan within a century!"

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s3_xuner.rpy:67
translate english ch1_s3_xuner_152ff3e3:

    # "是的，第二人，那位第一人，便是褪去了天才光环的萧炎。"
    "Yes, the second person. The first person was Xiao Yan, who had lost his genius halo."

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s3_xuner.rpy:72
translate english ch1_s3_xuner_8b1fc087:

    # xx "谢谢。"
    xx "Thank you."

# game/scripts/ch1/ch1_s3_xuner.rpy:74
translate english ch1_s3_xuner_bc830f08:

    # "少女微微点了点头，平淡的小脸并未因为他的夸奖而出现喜悦，安静的回转过身，然后在众人炽热的注目中，缓缓的行到了人群最后面的那颓废少年面前……"
    "The girl nodded slightly, her calm little face showing no joy because of his praise. She quietly turned around, and under everyone's burning gaze, slowly walked to the decadent boy at the very back of the crowd..."
